Titolo: Echoshift

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Echoshift is a 2009 puzzle video game for the PlayStation Portable and PlayStation Vita. The game uses events known as "Time Bounces" in which a small section of time repeats itself over and over again. By exploiting time bounces, the player can overcome various obstacles that would have been otherwise impossible to navigate. The game is a spinoff of the Echochrome series.

